    description:
      'Letting your AI agent directly manage API keys and call external services is a recipe for security incidents. Every new integration means another credential ...',
    source: 'awesome-openclaw',
    sourceUrl:
      'https://github.com/hesamsheikh/awesome-openclaw-usecases/blob/659895e58e2105c6db8fbef39f446c8a786a480c/usecases/n8n-workflow-orchestration.md',
